{"tid":631061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美英法空襲敘利亞 普京：若再攻敘利亞將釀全球混亂","createTime":"2018-04-16T06:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T09:13:55.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6675c85670ffce514b34ab58cd0fd569e5a24948","tid":631061,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美英法聯合空襲敘利亞，引發國際緊張，俄羅斯總統普廷在當地時間週日警告，西方若再進一步襲擊敘利亞，將為世界局勢帶來混亂。另一方面，美國華府則準備通過新的經濟制裁，以加大對俄羅斯的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，俄國克里姆林宮聲明指出，普廷稍早與伊朗總統羅哈尼（Hassan Rouhani）通電話，兩人都認為，西方空襲敘利亞，破壞了7年來敘利亞衝突中達成政治決議的機會。普廷針對英美法空襲作法表示，若這種違反聯合國憲章的行為繼續下去，那將不可避免的導致國際關係混亂繼續。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，美國駐聯合國大使海利（Nikki Haley）也表示，美國將在當地時間週一（台灣時間週二）宣布新的經濟制裁措施，制裁對象將是針對與敘利亞阿賽德政府有關的化武裝備產業。法國總統馬克宏則表示，法國已經說服了美國總統川普，讓美國軍隊「長時間」留在敘利亞。不過白宮隨即表示，川普仍希望在敘國的美軍能儘早撤回國。<br />\n<br />\n此外，敘利亞副外交部長梅克達德（Faisal Mekdad）與來自「禁止化學武器組織」（OPCW）的檢查人員，週日在敘利亞首都大馬士革會面約3小時，在場的還有俄國官員及一名高階敘國安全官員。OPCW檢查人員正在尋求前往據稱是這次敘國進行化武攻擊的度瑪鎮（Douma）現場調查。俄國則譴責，OPCW都還沒調查，西方國家就急著發動攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2396891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2396891&d=uVWShUs7fR7zWJwRkvKigL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2342ee4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2396891&h=2d961bbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2396891</a>"},{"pid":"32b6b625fe62795ba0fa2c19e1a137d01925c333","tid":631061,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SY2srwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSY2srwH.png&h=38182563&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"691cb8948f3c93a39ac8aa25357b2dfe79939d46","tid":631061,"uid":63669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暗示核戰"},{"pid":"16992bc9a7376f85ba4091f1f68b410e4ff86451","tid":631061,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"係有料既咪炸番美英法囉<br />\n驚咩?"},{"pid":"e640e824cbccc626175aa15bf21bc8d07a17860f","tid":631061,"uid":169728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"關我咩事？ 樓價又唔會跌既"},{"pid":"f9b8ef8a37f75f81e0cca1b7378fa6977fc0bef8","tid":631061,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"變左口交京<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7a377d5b0188b493782c73dc6f0290d379cf6b","tid":631061,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"左腸：｢唔好激嬲俄羅斯｣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ba18b496dbee55ec3dd7819bcaa8ff432156ef","tid":631061,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"廢柴京"},{"pid":"35ff0acdac93ff337cf19882532392b69f5d8b07","tid":631061,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}